## Phase 3：MapEditor 儲存邏輯更新

#### [MODIFY] [MapEditor.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MapEditor.cs)

**修改 `GetCurrentMapData()` 加上顯式轉換邏輯：**
- 由於編輯器內部（增刪節點、連線）仍依賴 `WaypointPaths` 及 index 陣列，存檔時需要將其轉換為 Node/Edge 格式：

```csharp
public MapData GetCurrentMapData()
{
    var result = new MapData
    {
        Ropes = _currentMapData.Ropes,
        SafeZones = _currentMapData.SafeZones,
        BoundaryMarkers = _currentMapData.BoundaryMarkers,
        WaypointPaths = _currentMapData.WaypointPaths,
        Connections = _currentMapData.Connections
    };

    // 把編輯器的內部 index 結構轉成 Nodes/Edges
    var indexToId = new Dictionary<int, string>();
    for (int i = 0; i < _currentMapData.WaypointPaths.Count; i++)
    {
        var wp = _currentMapData.WaypointPaths[i];
        if (wp.Length < 2 || wp[0] < 0) continue;
        var node = new NavNodeData { Id = $"n{i}", X = wp[0], Y = wp[1], Type = "Platform" };
        result.Nodes.Add(node);
        indexToId[i] = node.Id;
    }
    foreach (var conn in _currentMapData.Connections)
    {
        if (!indexToId.ContainsKey(conn[0]) || !indexToId.ContainsKey(conn[1])) continue;
        result.Edges.Add(new NavEdgeData
        {
            From = indexToId[conn[0]],
            To = indexToId[conn[1]],
            Action = ActionCodeToString(conn.Length > 3 ? conn[3] : 0),
            InputSequence = ActionCodeToInputSequence(conn.Length > 3 ? conn[3] : 0)
        });
    }
    return result;
}
```

> [!NOTE]
> MapEditor 內部的點位/連線管理邏輯（`_currentMapData.WaypointPaths` 等）不動，僅在匯出時建立 [Nodes](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/Domain/Navigation/NavigationGraph.cs#120-121)/[Edges](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#274-342)。這樣 Phase 1 (MapData) 也能順利編譯。

